title: NCS teams with Licking County Library to Grow Early Learners (Newark City School District)
text: ( Source : Newark City School District ) Newark City Schools and the Licking County Library are teaming up to offer a program for parents of young children, ages birth to 5. The Growing Early Learners program is hosting a event from 6 to 7
